slirpvde is based upon:

	slirp by Danny Gasparovsky
	slirp support for Qemu by Fabrice Bellard
	slirp-vde interface by Renzo Davoli

Important: I have had no time yet to write an autoconfiguration file.
Edit the Makefile to change CFLAGS depending on the endianess of your computer.

(Not tested yet on i386 but it should work)

